{"type": "article", "id": 35301, "title": "Burberry推出家居香薰，以及，Herschel的户外系列还不错 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2016-12-07T02:56:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 466, "name": "LVMH"}, {"id": 906, "name": "川久保玲"}, {"id": 2603, "name": "香氛"}, {"id": 20505, "name": "南方公园"}, {"id": 22806, "name": "Herschel"}, {"id": 31529, "name": "赫芬顿邮报"}, {"id": 35566, "name": "Burberyy"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 52, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161207102103xXBTWE3fQt8SPLmn.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://finance.yahoo.com/news/l-catterton-acquires-pinarello-leading-173700683.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>L Catterton 收购意大利高档自行车品牌 Pinarello</b></a> | 早在今年十月份，就传出 LVMH 有意通过旗下合资基金公司 L Catterton 收购 Pinarello 的消息。昨日，该消息确认属实，收购之后，Fausto Pinarello 将继续出任 Pinarello 的 CEO。</p><p><a href=\"http://www.cpp-luxury.com/sbe-acquires-morgans-hotel-group-for-805-million/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>高档酒店管理公司 SBE 收购 Morgans 酒店集团</b></a> | 上周，SBE 宣布完成对纽约精品酒店 Morgans 的收购，这笔交易价格为 8.05 亿美元。合并之后，SBE 一共经营 22 家酒店，拥有五个品牌的近 7000 间客房。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/media/victorias-secret-fashion-show-boosts-consumer-engagement-on-social-media-10720802/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>维多利亚的秘密引发社交网络话题</b></a> | 在周一，维多利亚的秘密在 Facebook 和 Twitter 上共被提及了 362000 次。</p><p class=\"\"><b>《<a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/media/lydia-polgreen-eic_huffington-post-10720830/\" rel=\"nofollow\">赫芬顿邮报》任命新主编</a></b> | Lydia Polgreen 离开纽约时报，继 Arianna Huffington 八月离职之后，成为了《赫芬顿邮报》的新一任主编。Lydia Polgreen 自 2002 年起为《纽约时报》工作，她的离职据说是为了寻求更好的机会，与《纽约时报》无关。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>继与 Nike Air Force 1 合作之后，<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/comme-des-garcons-holiday-emoji\" rel=\"nofollow\">川久保玲推出了 COMME des GARÇONS HOLIDAY EMOJI 完整系列</a>。该系列包括 T-shirt、连帽卫衣、棒球外套、风衣、手袋等，目前已经可由线下店铺购买。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612071005557k1LlJ5c39yNOMuo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161207100555Ox8Z1Wiomwnz0FDB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161207100555ldQmWw6GjZ5CD89N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161207100555dLminagqMe05hC6y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161207100555sfT6mnPKoy18dhOQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161207100555t6c1GzOAsCxS073J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161207100555jVRL6hayIDoFTONP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161207100556OfFPml3qSCWra0v1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161207100556m5xKvDzcUjbnPaoQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161207100556jetnOw680XvGVT3p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161207100556kWGRSNuKf2jvr0l5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161207100556spKSPE642qMYD170.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161207100556FOXcVYT41ULsvmM3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161207100556Cw2rQk0vYOt3zupa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/herschel-supply-co-2016-trail\" rel=\"nofollow\">Herschel Supply Co. 推出了户外防水 TRAIL 系列</a>，该系列采用了轻量化尼龙制作，并搭载防水外层。特别在  Mammoth、Barlow、Barlow Large 三款背包的底部设置了隐藏式的尼龙防雨罩，可以在下雨的时候迅速拉出保护背包。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161207100532qAUH25hOpvEX3Sox.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612071005322syFHL07iD9Enc1w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161207100532U9qdMAnXf0BxWcrh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612071005329lVFsmZi2yOnj5xS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161207100532gLzOFruRwl2bmqJC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161207100532Ko52nBuV8lgxN3ZF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161207100532jfx68IYAqHw2X5si.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612071005327eIhQ4OiuqJNWoAv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://popbee.com/lifestyle/home-and-living/burberry-home-collection/#\" rel=\"nofollow\">Burberry 推出全新的家居香薰系列</a>，该系列包括 6 款香薰蜡烛，2 款家居香薰喷雾和 3 款洗手液，香气由调香师 Francis Kurkdjian 设计，包含了玫瑰、野莓和草木的味道。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612071005101fMFWueKPJv3E4B9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612071005109u1AnqJTVDOlI6Hg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161207100510CimpgjUM0kadOKnr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612071005175BioPqeEXOgQFcUt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161207100517AGgrbhOJQXdcIn5K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161207100517NCE35KQleGTdcuri.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/nike-air-huarache-utility-premium-white-navy\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nike Air Huarache Utility 推出了全新配色版本</a>，新鞋采用了白色皮革制作鞋身，辅以「Midnight Navy」和「Gold」的细节，售价为 155 美元。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161207100453XGx2v16QHRLqMuNj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666956\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161207100453AGkLKtdFOivrx4po.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161207100453QarzecLqEovKRw08.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161207100501A2j4gXNROyt07Do1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>以人体工学设计、坚固耐用著称的单板滑雪品牌 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/burton-x-south-park\" rel=\"nofollow\">Burton，与经典动画《South Park》合作</a>，推出了假期联名系列。该系列包括了 T-shirt、帽子、袜子、单板、手套等多个单品，其中最有趣的莫过于主角四人的经典帽款。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016120710035794JIRNv3FQBc6TWx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.497110\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161207100357AYVoLKqSZice60fn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501449\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161207100357SZ5y0OmdPVuNIEaf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501449\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161207100358KETcj5Hnwg9tFNZh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501449\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612071003582ICP1BJLAwZn6kNh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501449\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161207100416QF40tPGByXH765mN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502294\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612071004234tp1IwYS0i2EO7K6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498856\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161207100423M2RkBTi7FVKPzjC8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498856\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p>"}